Package com.github.arachnidium.util.configuration.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IConfigurable
    It is for all objects which changes it is own options/parameters by given Configuration
    IConfigurationWrapper
    It is for all objects which stores given Configuration
    IHasPathToFile
    It is for all configurable/configuration entities which can return a path to some file
    IHasPathToFolder
    It is for all configurable/configuration entities which can return a path to some folder
